metadata.name: Childs-Nightmare-#2
metadata.description: Welcome to the world of my NFTs - a place where childhood nightmares come to life in vivid illustrations. With every piece, I strive to capture the essence of what makes us human - our emotions and our fears. Through a mix of traditional and AI-powered techniques, I turn my childhood nightmares into stunning pieces of art that tell stories of inner turmoil, courage and resilience. By bringing these nightmares to life, I hope to inspire others to explore the depths of their own creativity and push the boundaries of what's possible with art.
